<br>
I think what we have here now does show that indeed DPR happens before hit/miss...but there are a few fundimentals we have not covered yet:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Kailyn, the level of the mob and/or its atk value have absolutely nothing to do with D/P/R. The number of times that D/P/R fires is completely dependent on your skill level. No characteristic of an NPC will alter the percentage that you D/P/R.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
